Class TerminalPalette

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.lanterna.terminal.swing.TerminalPalette

  • public class TerminalPalette
extends Object
    This class specifies the palette of colors the terminal will use for the normally available 8 + 1.
    Author:
    Martin
